    Frequently Asked Questions

    How do I receive the bundle?

    After your purchase, you'll instantly receive a download link. This link allows you to download the bundle directly to your device. It's a quick and easy process, ensuring you can start using the tools immediately.

    Is this bundle suitable for beginners?

    Absolutely! This bundle is great for both professional artists and beginners. It's good for anyone interested in tattoo design, not just pros.

    How do I install the tools in Procreate?

    Installation is simple and straightforward. Our step-by-step guide walks you through the process, ensuring a smooth setup. Plus, if you encounter any issues, our customer support team is ready to help you get everything up and running.

    Can I use this bundle on multiple devices?

    You can use this bundle on any iOS device you own (iPad & iPhone), whether you're working in the studio or at home. However, please note that it cannot be used on PCs, laptops, or smartphones. This ensures optimal performance and compatibility with Procreate brushes designed specifically for tablet use.

    Is this a one-time payment?

    Yes. Our bundle is available as a one-time purchase. There are no recurring fees or subscriptions, so you pay once and enjoy the full benefits of the bundle for ALL your next designs!
